403
00:47:41,739 --> 00:47:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš ponesi u parkić dvije, tri igračke,

404
00:47:44,820 --> 00:47:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali imaš jednu koju ne daš nikome.

405
00:47:46,360 --> 00:47:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] I to je po meni ok.

406
00:47:47,019 --> 00:47:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] Daj dvije, jednu nemoj.

407
00:47:48,920 --> 00:47:53,179
