409
00:47:55,840 --> 00:47:58,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ili je prioritet da nauče ipak zamoliti, podijeliti?

410
00:47:58,699 --> 00:48:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] To je opet isto ples roditelstva.

411
00:48:01,280 --> 00:48:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ponekad ja zamolim djeta, ja onda učim stariju djecu.

412
00:48:03,679 --> 00:48:07,159
