414
00:48:10,340 --> 00:48:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa da ti se zamijenite.

415
00:48:11,300 --> 00:48:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto život, da ti nešto što hoćeš,

416
00:48:14,460 --> 00:48:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način dobiješ i da se toga potrudiš.

417
00:48:17,900 --> 00:48:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da to nekad uspije, nekad ne.

418
00:48:19,260 --> 00:48:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali recimo roditelji često griješe kad starijim,

419
00:48:21,480 --> 00:48:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] ti te to naređuju, moraš dijeliti s mlađim,

420
00:48:24,539 --> 00:48:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili moraš mu to dati jer to mlađe djete plače.

421
00:48:26,599 --> 00:48:27,179
[SPEAKER_00] To nije dobro.

422
00:48:27,179 --> 00:48:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znači stariji djete ne mora dijeliti stvari koje ne želi

423
00:48:30,619 --> 00:48:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] sa mlađim na temelju vaše direktivne upute.

424
00:48:33,619 --> 00:48:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je pa meni greška.

425
00:48:34,519 --> 00:48:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ponekad mi to napravimo, ponekad je to i ok da i stariji nauče dijeliti.

426
00:48:38,099 --> 00:48:39,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tu opet morate kao roditelj odvagnuti

427
00:48:39,719 --> 00:48:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] da li je sad bitno da djete prestane plakati,

428
00:48:42,400 --> 00:48:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] mlađe, je vam to bitnije

429
00:48:44,179 --> 00:48:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili vam je bitnije da oni imaju svoj odnos?

430
00:48:45,780 --> 00:48:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kad djeca imaju odnos, budu se oni dogovorili.

431
00:48:48,559 --> 00:48:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da isto kupovanje poklona,

432
00:48:51,420 --> 00:48:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] recimo moj Filip je sad neki dana prostavio peti rođendan,

433
00:48:53,579 --> 00:48:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] dobio je od nas, oni vole one metalne,

434
00:48:55,900 --> 00:48:56,780
[SPEAKER_00] autiće one velike,

435
00:48:56,780 --> 00:48:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ovaj Andrijica,

436
00:48:58,380 --> 00:49:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] on je plakao jer on želi, on nisi takav.

437
00:49:01,119 --> 00:49:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] On je prije tri mjeseca dobio svoj,

438
00:49:03,199 --> 00:49:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] kad je imao tri godine,

439
00:49:04,760 --> 00:49:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ja njemu kažem ljubavi,

440
00:49:05,739 --> 00:49:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali Filipov je rođendan,

441
00:49:06,960 --> 00:49:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] Filipov je poklon,

442
00:49:07,800 --> 00:49:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] ako Filip želi,

443
00:49:08,739 --> 00:49:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] on će dati,

444
00:49:09,599 --> 00:49:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad mu je to nova igračka,

445
00:49:11,079 --> 00:49:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] mora se on malo izigrati,

446
00:49:12,139 --> 00:49:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljite, razumiješ?

447
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] Onda on je njemu dao kasnije,

448
00:49:15,260 --> 00:49:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] on jako voli Andriju,

449
00:49:16,119 --> 00:49:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali Filip je odlučio da će mu dati autić,

450
00:49:18,579 --> 00:49:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] a onda, ne znam,

451
00:49:19,420 --> 00:49:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] dok ja odem na WC,

452
00:49:20,440 --> 00:49:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] evo tebi ti ga čuvaj.

453
00:49:21,940 --> 00:49:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tu zahtjeva puno roditeljske vještine,

454
00:49:25,199 --> 00:49:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] tu supruga odrađuje po mene super posao,

455
00:49:26,900 --> 00:49:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno jako dobar,

456
00:49:28,320 --> 00:49:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] dok se mene na poslu,

457
00:49:29,239 --> 00:49:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] i kad je ona više s djecom,

458
00:49:30,179 --> 00:49:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje,

459
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer ta su,

460
00:49:32,059 --> 00:49:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti to nekako suradnja,

461
00:49:33,320 --> 00:49:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je život,

462
00:49:33,880 --> 00:49:34,719
